Elsewhere: jekyll-feed



The stylin' archive
```
{{ for num in (1..100) }}
    {{ for post in site.posts | where_exp: "post.year == 2100 - num" }}
        {{ post.year }}, {{ post.month }}, {{ post.title }}, 
        and some other stuff
    {{ endfor }}
{{ endfor }}
```

